title: Bigoted Batman
description:
Bigoted Batman, written by Crystal Delahanty. Stone Cold Fox at Maude Night, UCBTNY, May 19, 2008.

Starring Scott Courlander, Fran Gillespie, Nate Lang, Cody Melton, and Joe Spellman. Directed by Neil W. Casey.
